description: Raoul Vargas is with us today being trained by Antony Lorca. It is a bit of a different style of video than normal as it was shot for us by guest director Vlado Iresch. The sex itself is not quite what we expected from this 'training' session. At times it verges on a little animalistic, even primitive where the only objective is a pleasure for both guys.
title: Bel Ami Update - Training Session
